<number id="3DAAC1449269FFDAFD13F8D3FD35F8E4" box="[715,730,1832,1858]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="4.0">4</number>
b) divided into two rectangular plates, with posterior angle acuminate; sclerotized rings (Fig. 
<number id="3DAAC1449269FFDAFDE3F8B6FDA4F8C1" box="[571,587,1869,1895]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" value="4.0">4</number>
c) simple, not twisted, with lateral margin thickened and anterior and posterior margins slender.
</paragraph>
